769px)\" srcset=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/home/title_kv_pc.png\">\n            <source media=\"(max-width:768px)\" srcset=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/home/title_kv_sp.png\">\n            <img src=\"https://www.cri.co.jp/recruit_info/theme_static/recruit/images/home/title_kv_pc.png\" alt=\"モノをつくる人と価値を作る仕事してみませんか\">\n        </picture>\n    </h1>\n    <div class=\"home-kv-slide\">\n        <div class=\"slide-item\">\n            <picture>\n                <source media=\"(min-width:769px)\" srcset=\"/recruit_info/2023_08/images/home_pc01.jpg\">\n                <source media=\"(max-width:768px)\" srcset=\"/recruit_info/2023_08/images/home_sp01.jpg\">\n                <img src=\"mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/2023_8/home_pc01.webp\" alt=\"\">\n            </picture>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"slide-item\">\n            <picture>\n                <source media=\"(min-width:769px)\" srcset=\"/recruit_info/2023_08/images/home_pc02.jpg\">\n                <source media=\"(max-width:768px)\" srcset=\"/recruit_info/2023_08/images/home_sp02.jpg\">\n                <img src=\"mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/2023_8/home_pc02.webp\" alt=\"\">\n            </picture>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"slide-item\">\n            <picture>\n                <source media=\"(min-width:769px)\" srcset=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/home/img_kv03_pc.png\">\n                <source media=\"(max-width:768px)\" srcset=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/home/img_kv03_sp.png\">\n                <img src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/home/img_kv03_pc.png\" alt=\"\">\n            </picture>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"slide-item\">\n            <picture>\n                <source media=\"(min-width:769px)\" srcset=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/home/img_kv04_pc.png\">\n                <source media=\"(max-width:768px)\" srcset=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/home/img_kv04_sp.png\">\n                <img src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/home/img_kv04_pc.png\" alt=\"\">\n            </picture>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"reminder-scroll\">\n        <span class=\"font-quattro\">SCROLL</span>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<section class=\"sec-faundation\">\n    <div class=\"l-inner\">\n        <h2 class=\"title-default has-read font-quattro bold title-animate\"><span>INTRODUCTION<span\n                    class=\"title-read\"><img src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/home/title_foundation.png\"\n                        alt=\"プロフェッショナルとともに\"></span></span></h2>\n        <div class=\"read\">\n            <p>幼い頃から傍にあったアニメやゲーム。<br>日常の中で何気なく目にする広告やWebサイト。<br>あの日、自分の背中を押してくれた映画や小説。</p>\n            <p>日々の暮らしが豊かになっていく裏側で、<br>これらを創り出している人を支えるために、<br>私たちは何ができるのか。</p>\n            <p>ジブンの答えで、応えていく。</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"sec-default\">\n    <figure><img src=\"/recruit_info/2023_08/images/about_us_ne01.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n    <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n        <h2 class=\"title-default title-animate\"><span class=\"font-quattro bold\">ABOUT US</span><small>会社情報</small></h2>\n        <p class=\"link-more\"><a href=\"/recruit_info/about_us/\" class=\"btn-base btn-main font-quattro bold\">VIEW MORE</a>\n        </p>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"sec-default top-story\">\n    <figure><img src=\"/recruit_info/2023_08/images/entrans.webp\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n    <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n        <h2 class=\"title-default title-animate\"><span class=\"font-quattro bold\">C&R STORY</span><small>創業者インタビュー</small>\n        </h2>\n        <p class=\"link-more\"><a href=\"/recruit_info/top_story/\" class=\"btn-base btn-main font-quattro bold\">VIEW\n                MORE</a></p>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"sec-default top-story\">\n    <figure><img src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/home/img_top-story.png\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n    <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n        <h2 class=\"title-default title-animate\"><span class=\"font-quattro bold\">TOP MESSAGE</span><small>社長メッセージ</small>\n        </h2>\n        <p class=\"link-more\"><a href=\"/recruit_info/top_message/\" class=\"btn-base btn-main font-quattro bold\">VIEW\n                MORE</a></p>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"sec-member\">\n    <div class=\"l-inner\">\n        <h2 class=\"title-default has-read font-quattro bold title-animate\"><span>MEMBER STORIES<span\n                    class=\"title-read\"><img src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/home/title_member-stories.png\"\n                        alt=\"キセキの舞台裏\"></span></span></h2>\n        <div class=\"member-slide\">\n            <div class=\"member-item\">\n                <a href=\"/recruit_info/member_stories/nishida/\">\n                    <img src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/home/img_member_01.png\" alt=\"\">\n                    <div class=\"read\">\n                        <p>ドキュメンタリー最高賞受賞！仕事嫌いな若手ディレクターを支えた「元作り手」エージェントの影の奮闘</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"arrow-link-icon\"></div>\n                </a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"member-item\">\n                <a href=\"/recruit_info/member_stories/takeuchi/\">\n                    <img src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/home/img_member_02.png\" alt=\"\">\n                    <div class=\"read\">\n                        <p>最悪の状況から逃げない！周囲を巻き込みTV不況の最中ながら信頼を得た、ある女性エージェントの話</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"arrow-link-icon\"></div>\n                </a>\n            </div>\n            <!-- div class=\"member-item\">\n                <a href=\"/recruit_info/member_stories/ishii/\">\n                    <img src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/home/img_member_03.png\" alt=\"\">\n            